D_{\exp}(m) & =\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{\mathrm{ad}_{m}^{j}}{(j+1)!}\label{eq:94}\\
 & =\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{(j+1)!}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
